snippet.title: Atari 2600 Codebreaker Game Cartridge, An Annotated Review
snippet.description: In 1978, Atari introduced Codebreaker, where you attempt to discover the hidden code in as few attempts as possible. For Numberpad Controller Only. Recorded with an Atari 2600 hooked up to the computer through a Tevion.
